title: Best of The Program | Guests: Sean Cahill & Sharyl Attkisson | 6/30/21
description:
Pat Gray joins to talk about the latest fugitive finally charged: a 69-year-old grandma who entered the Capitol on January 6. Climate protesters, including AOC and the Squad, blockaded the White House. UAP witness Sean Cahill joins to discuss the newly released UFO report and explain what he’s personally seen. Investigative reporter Sharyl Attkisson joins to review the NSA allegedly spying on Tucker Carlson and how the government could smear anybody it doesn’t like with the power it has.
